{"tid":207894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬學生哥啲錢邊到黎？","createTime":"2017-04-19T07:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T07:56:46.000Z","uid":68278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10f35b652bf51fd046dc597591822c04cbecb423","tid":207894,"uid":68278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"【有錢人調查】哪有錢！港「千萬富翁」 過千個係學生<br />\n<br />\n即時財經  2017-04-19 11:59:07 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n花旗銀行「香港千萬富翁調查2016」顯示，以21歲至79歲港人計算，2016年全香港有87.8萬名擁有百萬元以上流動資產的百萬富翁，按年升14%，創下歷史新高。至於千萬富翁，全港有5.9萬名，但按年並無增長。<br />\n<br />\n至於幾高人工先能夠踏上千萬富翁的階梯？統計指出，千萬富翁打工仔的月入中位數為17.5萬元！屬就業市場月入中位數的11倍。<br />\n<br />\n當中47%千萬富翁為打工仔，只有高級管理層、僱主同專業人士，其他冇份。非打工仔佔53%，退休人士佔整體四成，學生竟然佔千萬富翁的2%（約1,250名）！而主婦都有8.5%（約5,000名）左右。<br />\n<br />\n千萬富翁的流動資產中位數為2,000萬元，究竟佢哋持有乜嘢資產？有36%為現金（2015年為45%），27%為股票（2015年為30%），互惠基金及債券共佔三成。<br />\n<br />\n記者：江靖然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775b54ba98f0eb8f0fec1616e5a67604d099f5ae","tid":207894,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:36:51.000Z","msg":"有個億萬老豆就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4a71718101c2aedc944eac00cb2953705fa1a3","tid":207894,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"支那人走資"},{"pid":"4caa97ce69e8737b1adb56aa175830523b9a8733","tid":207894,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"啲女做雞月入十萬"},{"pid":"5abed0c0c3a458c3c9195a390fa2a8e9f7865494","tid":207894,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12a17cc1414129148d541ee2999894eae4792bd","tid":207894,"uid":106023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:41:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2336c8f7fc98d31ded2419819e20ab7ae150aa41","tid":207894,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲女做雞月入十萬</blockquote><br />\n要例夠十年過千萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪要八歲開始做？"},{"pid":"8c61151a68b8f1da8771bfe8988f9c4791564089","tid":207894,"uid":3739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"父幹或者母被幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db66daa3009f72388da1fe0b6e3de859252f278a","tid":207894,"uid":68278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家周街都有一百萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然一百萬真係好多人有<br />\n但係學生點先有一百萬<br />\n跪求方法"},{"pid":"bd7c4a06e28d761f6976ff0c006f2d55e17b48a7","tid":207894,"uid":68278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>父幹或者母被幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 呢啲機會"}]}